
// The code snippet uses the [and] slot to evaluate two conditions: it checks if a node named [summarize] exists within the [.arguments] node using [exists], and verifies if the value of this [summarize] node is equal to true using [eq]. If both conditions are true, the [and] slot evaluates to true.
and
   exists:x:@.arguments/*/summarize
   eq:x:@.arguments/*/summarize
      .:bool:true
